In Afghanistan, Barack Obama hopes that the miracle will repeat itself.
He was once again asked by the military, especially by the commander-in-chief of the Afghanistan operation General Stanley McCristal, who, despite the subordination habits, even harshly criticized the shady gunmen in the White House.
