That’s why almost 100% of reviewers use this type of system.
The service and application providers for the assessment of accidents and repair collect the information they receive from the manufacturers in order to process them afterwards and offer them to their customers in the form of a useful program.
In Spain, Audatex, part of the American group Solera, is the market leader; 80% of all reviews are produced with their products.
